{"lang": "ja_JP", "eventid": "act46side", "eventName": "聖山降臨1101", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "OS-8", "avgTag": "戦闘前", "storyName": "道半ばの宣告", "storyInfo": "カスター公爵が世論を煽動したことで、エンシオディスは不利な立場に追い込まれていく。\nヴィクトリアの記者は取材中、突如何者かの襲撃を受けて誘拐されてしまった。目覚めた彼女の目の前にいたのは、死んだはずのラタトスだった。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "45_g8_kjeragstreet", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$mist_intro", "key": "$mist_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "静寂と空虚さが、いっそう寒さを際立たせる中、記者は重いカバンを背負ってゆっくりと前に進んでいく。積雪を踏む足音がはっきりと響いていた。"}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2006_1#12$1", "afrom": 0.0, "ato": 1.0, "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2006_1#12$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "ここも随分人が減ったわね……", "name": "ヴィクトリアの記者"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2006_1#12$1"}, {"id": 15, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2006_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……あら？", "name": "ヴィクトリアの記者"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2006_1#6$1"}, {"id": 17, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "150,0", "duration": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.1}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_273_1$1", "afrom": 0.0, "ato": 1.0, "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2006_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.1}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "150,0", "duration": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2006_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "そちらのお嬢さん！　すみません、いくつか簡単な質問をさせていただいてもいいですか？", "name": "ヴィクトリアの記者"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2006_1#2$1"}, {"id": 29, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_273_1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "何よ、どうかしたの？", "name": "慌ただしげなイェラグ人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_273_1$1"}, {"id": 31, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2006_1#11$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "今のカランド貿易について――", "name": "ヴィクトリアの記者"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2006_1#11$1"}, {"id": 33, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_273_1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "その名前は聞きたくないわ。", "name": "慌ただしげなイェラグ人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_273_1$1"}, {"id": 35, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "エンシオディス様には、あの契約書に署名した経緯を説明していただきたいわよね。", "name": "慌ただしげなイェラグ人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_273_1$1"}, {"id": 36, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "「資源と引き換えに発展を得る」とかいうけど、結果的にはそれが今回の天災を招いたんじゃない？　その辺り、どう説明するつもりかしら？", "name": "慌ただしげなイェラグ人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_273_1$1"}, {"id": 37, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_273_1$1", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0, "posfrom": "150,0", "posto": "200,0", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "posfrom": "150,0", "posto": "0,0", "duration": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "ヴィクトリアの記者"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_273_1$1"}, {"id": 44, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2006_1#12$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2006_1#12$1", "focus": "none"}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "記者が向けられた怒りの言葉を消化しきれずにいるうちに、相手はとうに姿を消していた。"}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "-100,0", "duration": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.1}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_278_1$1", "afrom": 0.0, "ato": 1.0, "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2006_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "-70,0", "duration": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_278_1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2006_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……そちらの方、少しよろしいでしょうか！", "name": "ヴィクトリアの記者"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2006_1#2$1"}, {"id": 61, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_278_1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "あんた、ヴィクトリアの記者さんかね？", "name": "温和なイェラグ人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_278_1$1"}, {"id": 63, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "近頃のイェラグは物騒だから、地元の人だって家にこもってるくらいなんだよ。あんたも気を付けたほうがいい。", "name": "温和なイェラグ人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_278_1$1"}, {"id": 64, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2006_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "ご忠告に感謝いたします。ですがこんな時だからこそ、怖がっているわけにはいかないんです。そうでなければ、カメラを持つ資格なんてありませんから。", "name": "ヴィクトリアの記者"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2006_1#10$1"}, {"id": 66, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2006_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "今伺いたいのは、あなたがエンシオディス氏に抱いている率直な見解なのです。お聞かせ願えますか？", "name": "ヴィクトリアの記者"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2006_1#2$1"}, {"id": 68, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_278_1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "ううむ……あなたには悪いが、私はエンシオディス様がイェラグ人を欺いたのは確かだと思う一方で、ヴィクトリアにも疑わしい点があると思っている。", "name": "温和なイェラグ人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_278_1$1"}, {"id": 70, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "長年にわたり、私はイェラグがどう変化してきたかをこの目で見てきた。だから、エンシオディス様にも苦悩がなかったとは決して言えないのだ。", "name": "温和なイェラグ人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_278_1$1"}, {"id": 71, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "蔓珠院の大長老が出てきて話をしてくれたら良いのだが――", "name": "温和なイェラグ人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_278_1$1"}, {"id": 72, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_278_1$1", "focus": "all"}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2006_1#2$1", "focus": "all"}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_throwstone"}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_windowbreak"}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.2, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2006_1#6$1", "focus": "all"}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_278_1$1", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0, "posfrom": "-100,0", "posto": "-200,0", "focus": "all", "duration": 2.0}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2006_1#6$1", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "その時、突如飛んできた石が記者の鼻先をかすめて、背後のショーウィンドウを突き破った。"}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2006_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "middle", "type": "shake", "power": 2.0, "times": 70.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "きゃっ――", "name": "ヴィクトリアの記者"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2006_1#6$1"}, {"id": 88, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2006_1#6$1", "focus": "none"}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "ヴィクトリア人はイェラグから出ていけ！", "name": "激怒するイェラグ人"}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "イェラグの事情に無関係な人間が首を突っ込むな！", "name": "激怒するイェラグ人"}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.4, "xstrength": 40.0, "ystrength": 40.0, "vibrato": 40.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "まだ撮る気か？　さっさと出ていけ、この*イェラグスラング*！", "name": "激怒するイェラグ人"}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2006_1#12$1"}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2006_1#12$1", "focus": "none"}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "この瞬間、彼女はこれまでになく複雑な心境に陥った。"}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "彼女は、平凡な生活を送っていたイェラグの人々が、次第に疑り深くなり、苛立ちを抱えていくのを見てきていた。"}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "さらに、彼女はイェラグ滞在中に、心を許していた撮影班の仲間たちが彼女の部屋に忍び込み、原稿や写真を何度も調べていたのを見てしまうという経験もしていた。"}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2006_1#12$1"}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$rungeneral"}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2006_1#12$1", "posfrom": "-70,0", "posto": "150,0", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0, "duration": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "先ほど石を投げてきた男がもう一度石を手にしたところで、記者は取材相手に一礼すると現場を走り去った。"}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "逃げるしかないのだろうが、一体どこへ逃げたらいいのだろうか？"}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$m_dia_street_intro", "key": "$m_dia_street_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "67_G4_kjeragstreet", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$rungeneral"}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_2006_1#12$1", "posfrom": "-150,0", "posto": "0,0", "afrom": 0.0, "ato": 1.0, "duration": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2002_1$1", "afrom": 0.0, "ato": 1.0, "duration": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2002_1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "お姉ちゃん、ヴィクトリアの人？", "name": "イェラグの子供"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2002_1$1"}, {"id": 125, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_2006_1#4$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "あっ……ええ、そうよ。こんにちは、坊や。", "name": "ヴィクトリアの記者"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2006_1#4$1"}, {"id": 127, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_2006_1#12$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……君は、ヴィクトリア人が嫌いじゃないの？", "name": "ヴィクトリアの記者"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2006_1#12$1"}, {"id": 129, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2002_1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "うん、嫌いじゃないよ。", "name": "イェラグの子供"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2002_1$1"}, {"id": 131, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_2006_1#12$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2002_1$1"}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.1}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_2006_1#12$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "-150,0", "duration": 1.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_2006_1#12$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "posfrom": "-150,0", "posto": "0,0", "duration": 1.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_2006_1#12$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "少年の汚れた小さな手が、固くなったヴィクトリアのパンを差し出してきた。"}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2002_1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "だけど、パパはこれを捨てろって言うんだ。うちはヴィクトリアの人から施しなんて受けちゃダメなんだって。", "name": "イェラグの子供"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2002_1$1"}, {"id": 145, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_2006_1#12$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "じゃあ……", "name": "ヴィクトリアの記者"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2006_1#12$1"}, {"id": 147, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2002_1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "でも、イェラグの民は隣人を愛して、恩に報いなければならないっていうのがイェラガンドの教えだから。", "name": "イェラグの子供"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2002_1$1"}, {"id": 149, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "これはお姉ちゃんに返すね。", "name": "イェラグの子供"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2002_1$1"}, {"id": 150, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_walkfast"}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_2006_1#12$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2002_1#1$1", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "150,0", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0, "duration": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_2006_1#12$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_2006_1#12$1", "focus": "none"}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "足早に去っていく子供の背中を見つめる記者のまぶたは震え、彼女は喉に物でも詰まったような苦しさを覚えて、歯を食いしばっていた。"}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_2006_1#12$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_stickimp"}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 1.0, "g": 1.0, "b": 1.0, "fadetime": 0.3, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "curtain", "attributes": {"direction": 0.0, "fillfrom": 0.01, "fillto": 0.2, "grad": "true", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "curtain", "attributes": {"direction": 4.0, "fillfrom": 0.01, "fillto": 0.2, "grad": "true", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "focusout", "attributes": {"type": "bg", "id": "67_G4_kjeragstreet", "from": 0.0, "to": 1.0, "duration": 1.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "backgroundTween", "attributes": {"yFrom": 0.0, "yTo": 100.0, "xScaleFrom": 1.0, "xScaleTo": 1.1, "yScaleFrom": 1.0, "yScaleTo": 1.1, "duration": 5.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "curtain", "attributes": {"direction": 0.0, "fillfrom": 0.2, "fillto": 1.0, "grad": "true", "fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "curtain", "attributes": {"direction": 4.0, "fillfrom": 0.2, "fillto": 1.0, "grad": "true", "fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$bodyfalldown1"}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "彼女を車に乗せろ。見つからないようにな。", "name": "曖昧な声"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2006_1#12$1"}, {"id": 180, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "それが、意識を失う前の彼女が最後に聞いた声だった。"}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "curtain", "attributes": {"direction": 0.0, "fillfrom": 1.0, "fillto": 0.0, "grad": "true", "fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "curtain", "attributes": {"direction": 4.0, "fillfrom": 1.0, "fillto": 0.0, "grad": "true", "fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "focusout", "attributes": {"type": "bg", "from": 1.0, "to": 0.0, "duration": 0.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$m_dia_street_intro", "key": "$m_dia_street_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "45_g11_karlanheadquarters", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 190, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$dooropenquite"}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_172_svrash_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4114_harold_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 194, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4114_harold_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 196, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "エンシオディス様、またもお邪魔してしまい申し訳ない。", "name": "ハロルド"}, "figure_art": "avg_4114_harold_1#1$1"}, {"id": 197, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "このような有事には、私などよりほかの方に会うほうへ時間を割きたいとお思いになるでしょうが……", "name": "ハロルド"}, "figure_art": "avg_4114_harold_1#1$1"}, {"id": 198, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_172_svrash_1#10$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 199, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他人行儀な仰りようですね。", "name": "エンシオディス"}, "figure_art": "avg_172_svrash_1#10$1"}, {"id": 200, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "イェラグは今も、子爵殿のお心配りを忘れてはおりません。ゆえに以前から、お礼をお伝えする機会が欲しいと思っておりました。", "name": "エンシオディス"}, "figure_art": "avg_172_svrash_1#10$1"}, {"id": 201, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4114_harold_1#14$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 202, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "何を仰いますやら……私としても、このほどイェラグを再訪できたことには感無量の思いがございますよ。", "name": "ハロルド"}, "figure_art": "avg_4114_harold_1#14$1"}, {"id": 203, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "正直なところ、ここを訪れるたび、本当なら何か良い知らせを手に伺って、この老骨を雪山に捧げ、静かな余生を過ごしたいと思います。", "name": "ハロルド"}, "figure_art": "avg_4114_harold_1#14$1"}, {"id": 204, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4114_harold_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "ですが、現実には世は無常なもの。臨機応変な対応というものを学ばねばなりますまい。", "name": "ハロルド"}, "figure_art": "avg_4114_harold_1#1$1"}, {"id": 206, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_172_svrash_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 207, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "しかし、子爵殿はカスター公爵のために悪い知らせを伝えに来た、というわけではないのでしょう。", "name": "エンシオディス"}, "figure_art": "avg_172_svrash_1#1$1"}, {"id": 208, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4114_harold_1#11$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 209, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "ええ。あのお婆さんのことには、私もこれ以上関わりたくはありませんからね。", "name": "ハロルド"}, "figure_art": "avg_4114_harold_1#11$1"}, {"id": 210, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4114_harold_1#14$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 211, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "それに、前回私がイェラグに来た時の状況を鑑みるに……彼女は私の介入を望んではいないでしょう。", "name": "ハロルド"}, "figure_art": "avg_4114_harold_1#14$1"}, {"id": 212, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_172_svrash_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "ところで、子爵殿……", "name": "エンシオディス"}, "figure_art": "avg_172_svrash_1#1$1"}, {"id": 214, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4114_harold_1#4$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 215, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "おお、そうですな、本題に入りましょう。貴方もお忙しいでしょうから。", "name": "ハロルド"}, "figure_art": "avg_4114_harold_1#4$1"}, {"id": 216, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4114_harold_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "この度は、お別れを言いに来たのです。", "name": "ハロルド"}, "figure_art": "avg_4114_harold_1#1$1"}, {"id": 218, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_172_svrash_1#2$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 219, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "近頃のヴィクトリア関連の世論が子爵殿にご迷惑をおかけしたということであれば、私のほうで――", "name": "エンシオディス"}, "figure_art": "avg_172_svrash_1#2$1"}, {"id": 220, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4114_harold_1#6$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "ああ、いやいや……それだけの話ではないのです。", "name": "ハロルド"}, "figure_art": "avg_4114_harold_1#6$1"}, {"id": 222, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4114_harold_1#11$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 223, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……元々私は、あのお婆さんもそろそろ年を取って少しは丸くなったのではと、少々非現実的な期待を抱いておりました。", "name": "ハロルド"}, "figure_art": "avg_4114_harold_1#11$1"}, {"id": 224, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4114_harold_1#8$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "そうであれば多少の善意を示すこともあったでしょう。ですが、結果はご覧の有様です。", "name": "ハロルド"}, "figure_art": "avg_4114_harold_1#8$1"}, {"id": 226, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4114_harold_1#3$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "ゆえに、耄碌したと思われるかもしれませんが、どうしても貴方に直接お尋ねしたいと思いまして。", "name": "ハロルド"}, "figure_art": "avg_4114_harold_1#3$1"}, {"id": 228, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4114_harold_1#12$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 229, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "本当に、他の方法はなかったのですか？", "name": "ハロルド"}, "figure_art": "avg_4114_harold_1#12$1"}, {"id": 230, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_172_svrash_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 231, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "子爵殿もご存知の通り、彼女の狙いはいくつかの採掘場だけには留まらぬものです。", "name": "エンシオディス"}, "figure_art": "avg_172_svrash_1#1$1"}, {"id": 232, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_172_svrash_1#9$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 233, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "エンシアに手を出された時点で、私にとってこの協議は受け入れられぬものとなりました。", "name": "エンシオディス"}, "figure_art": "avg_172_svrash_1#9$1"}, {"id": 234, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4114_harold_1#15$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 235, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "ではどう対処なさるおつもりで？　まさか本気で彼女と刃を交えようとでも？", "name": "ハロルド"}, "figure_art": "avg_4114_harold_1#15$1"}, {"id": 236, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_172_svrash_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 237, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "最後の一線として「刃を交える」可能性を示していなければ、イェラグはとうに彼女の手中に落ちていたかもしれないということは、子爵殿のほうがよくお分かりのはずでしょう。", "name": "エンシオディス"}, "figure_art": "avg_172_svrash_1#1$1"}, {"id": 238, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4114_harold_1#11$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "ハロルド", "content": "それはそうですが……"}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4114_harold_1#16$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "ハロルド", "content": "やれやれ、何と言ったものでしょうか。"}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4114_harold_1#3$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 243, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "彼女の性格を思うに、ここまで来たら簡単には引き下がってくれませんよ。", "name": "ハロルド"}, "figure_art": "avg_4114_harold_1#3$1"}, {"id": 244, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4114_harold_1#11$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 245, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "私は心の底から貴方を案じているのです、エンシオディス様。この先どうしたものでしょうね。", "name": "ハロルド"}, "figure_art": "avg_4114_harold_1#11$1"}, {"id": 246, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_172_svrash_1#2$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 247, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "「成り行きに従う」ほかありますまい。", "name": "エンシオディス"}, "figure_art": "avg_172_svrash_1#2$1"}, {"id": 248, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_172_svrash_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "時に、子爵殿も、カスター公爵とは旧知の仲でいらっしゃるのですか？", "name": "エンシオディス"}, "figure_art": "avg_172_svrash_1#1$1"}, {"id": 250, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4114_harold_1#7$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "ハロルド", "content": "私ですか？"}}, {"id": 252, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4114_harold_1#6$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 253, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "ハロルド", "content": "　いやいや、そんなとんでもない。"}}, {"id": 254, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4114_harold_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 255, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "数年前までは世間話くらいはしていましたが、そうした時は常々カスター家の若者のことを話題にしては、出来の良い子が一人もいないと愚痴っていましたよ。", "name": "ハロルド"}, "figure_art": "avg_4114_harold_1#1$1"}, {"id": 256, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4114_harold_1#14$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 257, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "そして、若者たちの出来が悪くなるほどに、彼女は焦った手を打つようになったものです。あれでは、若かりし頃の底知れぬ彼女のことなど誰に想像できましょうか。", "name": "ハロルド"}, "figure_art": "avg_4114_harold_1#14$1"}, {"id": 258, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_172_svrash_1#4$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 259, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "十年以上前、一度公爵にお会いした際の気高いお姿は、今も目に焼き付いておりますよ。", "name": "エンシオディス"}, "figure_art": "avg_172_svrash_1#4$1"}, {"id": 260, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4114_harold_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 261, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "ははっ、私にそのような物言いをする必要はありませんよ。", "name": "ハロルド"}, "figure_art": "avg_4114_harold_1#1$1"}, {"id": 262, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4114_harold_1#4$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 263, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "あの傲慢でいかにも貴族ぶった態度は昔から変わらぬものでしょうしな。", "name": "ハロルド"}, "figure_art": "avg_4114_harold_1#4$1"}, {"id": 264, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4114_harold_1#14$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 265, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "何しろ、裏でどれだけ策略を巡らせていようとも、人前に立てばそうした素振りを見せず、いかにも尊大で威厳ある姿勢を保たねばならないのですから。", "name": "ハロルド"}, "figure_art": "avg_4114_harold_1#14$1"}, {"id": 266, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 267, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4114_harold_1#14$1", "focus": "none"}}, {"id": 268, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$doorknockquite"}}, {"id": 269, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 270, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4114_harold_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 271, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_172_svrash_1#11$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 272, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……さて、貴方の部下にはより重要な用件がおありのようですし、私はそろそろお暇いたしましょう。", "name": "ハロルド"}, "figure_art": "avg_4114_harold_1#1$1"}, {"id": 273, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_172_svrash_1#11$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 274, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……子爵殿との意見交換は大変勉強になりました。", "name": "エンシオディス"}, "figure_art": "avg_172_svrash_1#11$1"}, {"id": 275, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_172_svrash_1#10$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 276, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "またいずれ、より適切な時期にあなたをイェラグへお招きできたらと思います。", "name": "エンシオディス"}, "figure_art": "avg_172_svrash_1#10$1"}, {"id": 277, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4114_harold_1#4$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 278, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "ははっ、それは有難い！", "name": "ハロルド"}, "figure_art": "avg_4114_harold_1#4$1"}, {"id": 279, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4114_harold_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 280, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "おっと、そうでした……", "name": "ハロルド"}, "figure_art": "avg_4114_harold_1#1$1"}, {"id": 281, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4114_harold_1#6$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 282, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（声を抑える）公爵様にお会いになった際は、私が彼女を陰で「お婆さん」呼ばわりしていたことはくれぐれもご内密にお願いいたします。", "name": "ハロルド"}, "figure_art": "avg_4114_harold_1#6$1"}, {"id": 283, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_172_svrash_1#10$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 284, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……無論そのように。", "name": "エンシオディス"}, "figure_art": "avg_172_svrash_1#10$1"}, {"id": 285, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4114_harold_1#6$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 286, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "ありがとうございます。", "name": "ハロルド"}, "figure_art": "avg_4114_harold_1#6$1"}, {"id": 287, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4114_harold_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 288, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "それでは、またイェラグを訪れる機会があるよう、私も心から願っております。", "name": "ハロルド"}, "figure_art": "avg_4114_harold_1#1$1"}, {"id": 289, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 290, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 291, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 292, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 293, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 294, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "24_g5_guestroom", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 295, "prop": "focusout", "attributes": {"type": "bg", "id": "24_g5_guestroom", "from": 1.0, "to": 1.0, "duration": 0.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 296, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 297, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……"}}, {"id": 298, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "はい、誰にも気付かれていません。", "name": "曖昧な声"}}, {"id": 299, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "大丈夫です、必ずやご要望通り……", "name": "曖昧な声"}}, {"id": 300, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "すぐに彼女を連れていきます。", "name": "曖昧な声"}}, {"id": 301, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……"}}, {"id": 302, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "おい、起きろ！", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 303, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 304, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 305, "prop": "curtain", "attributes": {"direction": 0.0, "fillfrom": 1.0, "fillto": 0.4, "grad": "true", "fadetime": 3.0}}, {"id": 306, "prop": "curtain", "attributes": {"direction": 4.0, "fillfrom": 1.0, "fillto": 0.4, "grad": "true", "fadetime": 3.0}}, {"id": 307, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.0}}, {"id": 308, "prop": "curtain", "attributes": {"direction": 0.0, "fillfrom": 0.4, "fillto": 0.0, "grad": "true", "fadetime": 3.0}}, {"id": 309, "prop": "curtain", "attributes": {"direction": 4.0, "fillfrom": 0.4, "fillto": 0.0, "grad": "true", "fadetime": 3.0}}, {"id": 310, "prop": "focusout", "attributes": {"type": "bg", "id": "24_g5_guestroom", "from": 1.0, "to": 0.0, "duration": 2.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 311, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.0}}, {"id": 312, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2006_1#12$1", "afrom": 0.0, "ato": 1.0, "duration": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 313, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 314, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2006_1#12$1"}}, {"id": 315, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$darkalley_intro", "key": "$darkalley_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 316, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……ここは……私は、確か――", "name": "ヴィクトリアの記者"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2006_1#12$1"}, {"id": 317, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_284_1$1"}}, {"id": 318, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "半日寝たのにまだ寝足りないのか？　さっさと起きろ。当主様からお前に話があるんだ。", "name": "ブラウンテイルの衛兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_284_1$1"}, {"id": 319, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2006_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 320, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "何を……", "name": "ヴィクトリアの記者"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2006_1#11$1"}, {"id": 321, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2006_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 322, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "当主様って……？", "name": "ヴィクトリアの記者"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2006_1#11$1"}, {"id": 323, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 324, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "ったく、あんたと来たら、いつになったら加減を覚えるんだい？", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2006_1#11$1"}, {"id": 325, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_284_1$1"}}, {"id": 326, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "も、申し訳ありません。", "name": "ブラウンテイルの衛兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_284_1$1"}, {"id": 327, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "ラタトス様。", "name": "ブラウンテイルの衛兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_284_1$1"}, {"id": 328, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 329, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 330, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_253_1#1$1", "afrom": 0.0, "ato": 1.0, "duration": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 331, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 332, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "よう、目は覚めたかい？", "name": "ラタトス"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#1$1"}, {"id": 333, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_253_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 334, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "動くんじゃないよ。手首の縄が食い込んでもいいなら話は別だけどね。", "name": "ラタトス"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#5$1"}, {"id": 335, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2006_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 336, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "ヴィクトリアの記者"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2006_1#2$1"}, {"id": 337, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2006_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 338, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "えっ、ラタトスさん！？", "name": "ヴィクトリアの記者"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2006_1#6$1"}, {"id": 339, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2006_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 340, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……じゃなくてラタトス様、私はてっきり――", "name": "ヴィクトリアの記者"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2006_1#6$1"}, {"id": 341, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_253_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 342, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "焦げ一つない私を見て驚いたかい？", "name": "ラタトス"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#1$1"}, {"id": 343, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_253_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 344, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "機会があったら同僚に教えてやるんだね。ブラウンテイル家に関わる時は、部屋の仕掛けを確かめろって。", "name": "ラタトス"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#4$1"}, {"id": 345, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2006_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 346, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "同僚……ですか？", "name": "ヴィクトリアの記者"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2006_1#11$1"}, {"id": 347, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_253_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 348, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "正直に言いな。何日もコソコソ嗅ぎまわって、何を撮ろうとしてたんだ、スパイさん？", "name": "ラタトス"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#9$1"}, {"id": 349, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2006_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 350, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "なっ……誤解です！　私がスパイだなんて！", "name": "ヴィクトリアの記者"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2006_1#6$1"}, {"id": 351, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_253_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 352, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "はぁ……", "name": "ラタトス"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#2$1"}, {"id": 353, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_253_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 354, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "捕まったスパイは皆そう言うんだよ。", "name": "ラタトス"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#5$1"}, {"id": 355, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 356, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_paper1"}}, {"id": 357, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "彼女のそばにいた衛兵が、記者のリュックから何かを取り出し、床に放り投げた。それは彼女がこの数日で撮影し、現像した写真だった。"}}, {"id": 358, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_253_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 359, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "風土や暮らしぶり、あとは巡回中の衛兵を多少撮るくらいなら別にわざわざ構いやしないさ。", "name": "ラタトス"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#5$1"}, {"id": 360, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_253_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 361, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "だが、あんたには遠慮ってもんがない。蔓珠院で勝手に写真を撮ったばかりか、あちこちの山に登っては撮影していたね。", "name": "ラタトス"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#7$1"}, {"id": 362, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "私が何も知らないとは思わないことだ。", "name": "ラタトス"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#7$1"}, {"id": 363, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2006_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 364, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "ヴィクトリアの記者"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2006_1#9$1"}, {"id": 365, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2006_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 366, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "ラタトス様、信じてもらえないかもしれませんが、私は本当にただの記者なんです。", "name": "ヴィクトリアの記者"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2006_1#2$1"}, {"id": 367, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2006_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 368, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "仮にスパイであれば、こんな証拠を持ったまま街を歩いたりすると思いますか？", "name": "ヴィクトリアの記者"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2006_1#10$1"}, {"id": 369, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2006_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 370, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "それに、今の混乱した状況を考慮すれば、テレビ局の同僚に資料をすべて預けて保管してもらうことだって考えられたはずですよね。", "name": "ヴィクトリアの記者"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2006_1#10$1"}, {"id": 371, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_253_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 372, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "その理由についてはあんた自身に説明してもらいたいね。", "name": "ラタトス"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#9$1"}, {"id": 373, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_253_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 374, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "事実、あんたは大量に怪しい資料を持ち歩き、不審な行動を取っていたんだから。逃げようとしていたと思われても仕方ないだろう？", "name": "ラタトス"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#7$1"}, {"id": 375, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.2, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 40.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 376, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2006_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 377, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "それは資料を守っていたからです！", "name": "ヴィクトリアの記者"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2006_1#7$1"}, {"id": 378, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2006_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 379, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "カスター公爵が世論統制を始めて以降、報道局から撮影班に派遣されてきた人員が、私の撮影した映像を勝手に削除したり、編集したり、私の部屋を調べたりしてきたんです。", "name": "ヴィクトリアの記者"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2006_1#10$1"}, {"id": 380, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2006_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 381, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "私があの場から逃げ出していなければ、あなたが目にした素材のほとんどは彼らに没収され、最終的には内容を歪められて使われていたことでしょう。", "name": "ヴィクトリアの記者"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2006_1#10$1"}, {"id": 382, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2006_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 383, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "彼らは、ヴィクトリアがイェラグの内政へ強制介入する行為を正当化するためにそんなことをしているんです！", "name": "ヴィクトリアの記者"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2006_1#7$1"}, {"id": 384, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_253_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 385, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "ラタトス"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#2$1"}, {"id": 386, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2006_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 387, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "この素材がイェラグのために役立つとお思いになるのなら、私はあなたにすべてを託しても構いません。", "name": "ヴィクトリアの記者"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2006_1#10$1"}, {"id": 388, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2006_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 389, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "ヴィクトリアの記者", "content": "この資料を公表し、より多くの人に、今のイェラグで起きていることを伝えてくださるなら……"}}, {"id": 390, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2006_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 391, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "ヴィクトリアの記者", "content": "何しろ、イェラグに必要なのはヴィクトリア人の「施し」ではなく、本当の助けですから！"}}, {"id": 392, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_253_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 393, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "ラタトス"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#2$1"}, {"id": 394, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_253_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 395, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "厄介なことになったな。", "name": "ラタトス"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#5$1"}, {"id": 396, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_253_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 397, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "こんな時だが、エンシオディスの奴は電話に出られるもんかね。", "name": "ラタトス"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#9$1"}, {"id": 398, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 399, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 400, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 401, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$dooropenquite"}}, {"id": 402, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 403, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 404, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4116_blkkgt_1#1$1", "posfrom": "-200,0", "posto": "0,0", "afrom": 0.0, "ato": 1.0, "duration": 1.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 405, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 406, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "悪いけど、彼にはもっと大事な用事があるの。だから、応援に来たのは私だけよ。", "name": "デーゲンブレヒャー"}, "figure_art": "avg_4116_blkkgt_1#1$1"}, {"id": 407, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_253_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 408, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "私は自分の死を偽装したあと、何人かのスパイを捕らえてあいつに引き渡した。約束通りなら、とっくにこっちへ応援を寄こしていい頃だってのに。", "name": "ラタトス"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#4$1"}, {"id": 409, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "ラタトス", "content": "結局寄こしたのはたった一人。ただし、それが黒騎士ときた。"}}, {"id": 410, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_253_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 411, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "ラタトス", "content": "太っ腹なのかケチなのか……"}}, {"id": 412, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4116_blkkgt_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 413, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "デーゲンブレヒャー"}, "figure_art": "avg_4116_blkkgt_1#7$1"}, {"id": 414, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_253_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 415, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "それでカスター公爵への対処だが、あいつに何か策はあるのかい？", "name": "ラタトス"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#4$1"}, {"id": 416, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4116_blkkgt_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 417, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "今は敵の情報を集めているところよ。あなたの尋問の手伝いとして私が来たのもそのためなの。", "name": "デーゲンブレヒャー"}, "figure_art": "avg_4116_blkkgt_1#11$1"}, {"id": 418, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4116_blkkgt_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 419, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "今一番肝心なのは、この記者が「山にある物」を撮ったかどうか。", "name": "デーゲンブレヒャー"}, "figure_art": "avg_4116_blkkgt_1#6$1"}, {"id": 420, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_253_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 421, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "それじゃ、そこの記者。", "name": "ラタトス"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#1$1"}, {"id": 422, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_253_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 423, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "まずはあんたの拘束を緩めてやるよ。だから約束することだ。", "name": "ラタトス"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#10$1"}, {"id": 424, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_253_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 425, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "この先聞かれたことには必ず答えると。いいね？", "name": "ラタトス"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#11$1"}, {"id": 426, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 427, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 428, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 429, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 430, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 431, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 432, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}